| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1635 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff5b61ce-b1d2-5e55-9dec-d1d359a90a91"
